arena-ghost-role-fighter-description =
    A participant in a duel arena. The map and loadout are randomly assigned before each match.
    Once the countdown ends, the barriers come down and the one-on-one fight begins. The last fighter standing is declared the winner.
arena-ghost-role-fighter-rules =
    The character has no connection to the station and is not involved in its internal conflicts. Any interaction outside the arena is prohibited.
    Stalling the fight, avoiding your opponent, or ghosting out during the countdown or match in order to disrupt the round is not allowed.

